.TH d2b-clipboard-arm 1 1970-01-01 d2b "d2b CLI"
.SH NAME
arm \- Arm the fallback two\-step paste workflow (Mod+Shift+V → Ctrl+V)
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBarm\fR [\fB\-\-json\fR] [\fB\-\-human\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Arm the fallback two\-step paste workflow (Mod+Shift+V → Ctrl+V).
.PP
Opens the d2b\-clip\-picker, waits for a selection, then arms d2b\-clipd to satisfy the next native paste request from the current focused window. Requires d2b\-clipd to be running.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-json\fR

.TP
\fB\-\-human\fR

.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
